                     <interp inst="t17861025-109-off603" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17861025-109-cd604" type="crimeDate">15th day of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861025-109-off603 t17861025-109-cd604"></join>, one silver watch, value 40 s. a chain, value 2 d. a seal, value 2 d. a key, value 1 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17861025-109-victim1329" type="victimName">
                     Benjamin 
                     Coombes
                  <interp inst="t17861025-109-victim1329" type="surname" value="Coombes"></interp>
